These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: satire, family, animation, crime, horror
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: house, blues, salsa, hip-hop, metal
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
4. the person watching family movies is on the far left##1
5. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
6. the person watching satire movies is in the middle##1
7. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| Movie-Genre   | family | animation | satire | horror | crime |
| Music-Genre   | metal    | house | salsa     | hip-hop       | blues  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: lemonade, 7up, juice, hot-chocolate, water
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, soul, punk, classical, pop
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the fan of soul##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle##1
5. the person drinking 7up is the fan of punk##1
6. the fan of pop is the person drinking water##1
7. the fan of classical is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| Beverage      | 7up | juice | lemonade | hot-chocolate | water |
| Music-Genre   | punk  | classical   | dubstep       | soul    | pop   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
There 5 different types of food: spinach, pomegranate, potato, tomato, artichoke
The people use 5 different means of transport: snowmobile, airplane, train, scooter, van
1. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person driving the van##1
3. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person eating potato is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the train##1
6. the person eating pomegranate is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Food        | potato | tomato | pomegranate | spinach | artichoke |
| Transport   | airplane  | snowmobile      | van | train | scooter      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: drawing, gardening, chess, singing, photography
The people have 5 different jobs:  dressmaker, manager, designer, dancer, photographer
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the manager##1
2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the manager##1
3. the dancer is on the right of the dressmaker##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the photographer##1
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
6. the designer is on the far right##1
7. the photographer is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Hobby   | singing    | drawing        | chess | gardening | photography |
| Job     | dressmaker | dancer | photographer  | manager   | designer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
There 5 different types of food: peas, eggplant, apricot, lime, lemon
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skateboarding, golf, cycling, skiing, surfing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is the person eating lemon##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person eating lime##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is in the middle##1
5. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating peas##1
6. the person who's sport is surfing is the person eating lime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| Food    | apricot   | peas     | eggplant   | lime         | lemon |
| Sport   | skateboarding | skiing | cycling | surfing | golf     |

