.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: snowboarding, vaning, ice-hockey, golf, parkour
The people use 5 different means of transport: jet-ski, airplane, boat, ship, van
1. the person driving the ship is in the middle##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
4. the person driving the boat is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is vaning##1
6. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| Sport       | golf   | ice-hockey   | vaning | parkour | snowboarding |
| Transport   | airplane | boat | ship   | van | jet-ski       |

