.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
5 different pets are kept: bird, turtle, guinea-pig, horse, goat
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: lacrosse, snowboarding, weightlifting, swimming, sailing
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in the middle##1
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| Pet     | turtle   | guinea-pig  | goat      | bird | horse     |
| Sport   | swimming | weightlifting | snowboarding | lacrosse   | sailing |

