3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the nurse is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
6. the doctor is on the right of the designer##1
7. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the coach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Job     | designer | doctor       | nurse | coach | videographer    |
| Sport   | skateboarding   | swimming | lacrosse  | parkour     | climbing |

