.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-11::.
There 5 different types of food: corn, radish, cranberry, garlic, spinach
5 different pets are kept: mouse, pony, horse, hamster, rat
1. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the owner of the pony is the person eating garlic##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
4. the person eating corn is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
5. the person eating spinach is on the far right##1
6. the person eating spinach is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
7. the owner of the rat is the person eating cranberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |      5      |
| Food   | garlic | corn  | cranberry | radish | spinach |
| Pet    | pony    | hamster | rat   | mouse       | horse        |

