6. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person eating onion##1
7. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3     |    4    |    5    |
| Food    | pomegranate | cucumber          | avocado    | cranberry | onion  |
| Sport   | sailing  | swimming | climbing | skiing | baseball |

