4. the indonesian is the person driving the van##1
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the nigerian##1
6. the malaysian is in the middle##1
7. the malaysian is on the right of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |    4     |    5    |
