.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-18::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, horror, fantasy, animation, western
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: lacrosse, soccer, parkour, volleyball, surfing
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is in the middle##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
4. the person watching western movies is the person who's sport is surfing##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4      |    5     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror   | animation  | documentary | western | fantasy  |
| Sport         | lacrosse | parkour | volleyball  | surfing    | soccer |

