.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-19::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, almond-milk, lemonade, iced-tea
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: volleyball, baseball, golf, parkour, badminton
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |   4    |    5     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea     | almond-milk       | juice     | sprite  | lemonade  |
| Sport      | parkour | volleyball | baseball | badminton | golf |

