.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-20::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: western, family, disaster, animation, sports
5 different pets are kept: ferret, turtle, goldfish, guinea-pig, fish
1. the owner of the turtle is in the middle##1
2. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
6. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Movie-Genre   | family | sports | disaster | western | animation |
| Pet           | fish | guinea-pig  | turtle    | ferret  | goldfish   |

 